messages.message: You’re basically looking for a mini UAT? I’ve heard that in the past we basically run through all our standard demos (Sheet, Refiner, NLP, Diff etc), we can also run through the “Instabase U” training topics, but I don’t know if we have that really formalized. I think that’s a great idea! Very happy to help in creating one after solutions interviews wrap up, since I think it’s actually complementary to what we’ll need to train these engineers on.
Yes, a mini-UAT. I will love to have Instabase pass through a checklist before we handoff to business teams.
